data.value:
In the Downtown Dubai district of Dubai, close to Dubai Mall, Heaven Crest Holiday Homes - Luxury Forte has pool with a view and a washing machine . This property offers access to a terrace and free private parking. The property is 600 metres from the city centre and 700 metres from Burj Khalifa.
The air-conditioned apartment is composed of 2 separate bedrooms, a living room, a fully equipped kitchen, and 2 bathrooms. A flat-screen TV is offered. The accommodation is non-smoking . The Dubai Fountain is 1.4 km from the apartment, while City Walk Mall is 3.9 km from the property. The nearest airport is Dubai International Airport, 14 km from Heaven Crest Holiday Homes - Luxury Forte.
